# SpriteSheet

A small helper class to convert .gifs to sprites that can be used by other
Frameworks suchs as EaselJS.

    Work In Progress!

## Usage

      sheet = Sheet.new("example.gif")
      sheet.write_to("example_sheet.jpg")

powered by `RMagick`

